段一．
Their art consists of handling it correctly,and managing it just as they wish through flattering it and carefully suiting themselves to its varying moods.
1.他们的艺术包含了正确的处理他们，和像预想的那样通过奉承他们并且细心的使他们适应变化的情绪。
