According to Plato,we thereby destroy the foundation of his authority:for it does not depend on any mystic personal leadership,but on the power of the truth to convince.
1.柏拉图认为，这样是在破坏他统治的基础，因为这种统治不依赖任何杰出的个人领导力，靠的是坚信真理的力量。

